  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5935178">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5935178/" class="title-link">老兵不死</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5935178"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/i243/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u35808866-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/i243/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">yut</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-07"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-07 16:32:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5935178_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   “老兵不死， 只是慢慢消逝。 老兵不惧怕死亡， 他们只怕被慢慢遗忘。” 拿到书以后才知道，这本《飞虎传奇----美国志愿援华航空队影像档案》实际上是云南卫视《经典人文地理》栏目组推出的十二集大型史诗纪录片《飞虎传奇》的同步书籍，同时也是时代华语推出的“向老兵致敬系...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
